5. Nc6 {Many strong GMs have made this mistake.} 
6. Nb5
6. g6
7. Qf3
7. f5
8. Qd5
8. Qe7
9. Nxc7+
9. Kd8
10. Nxa8
10. b6 {Black obviously didn't want this position but we still need to be cautious due to our lack of development and tender queen.} 
11. Ne2 {11.Nf3?an example of White not being cautious about their queen.11...Bb712.d3Nd4∓this is an example of how Black can turn things around here.} 
11. Bb7
12. Qd3 {Get her worship out of danger!} 
12. Bxa8
13. O-O {Black can try many things here but ultimately we will eventually get our pieces out, if Black's king were safe they might have compensation for the exchange.} 
