10. Nh6
11. a4
11. Bc4
12. Na3 {Our bad knight finds a job!} 
12. Nd7
13. b5
13. Qa5
14. Nxc4
14. dxc4
15. O-O {Black's queen is cut from the defense, and no, she can't take c3 as Bd2 traps the lady. We have the bishops, Black's h6-knight is terrible, and ...O-O isn't possible yet because the knight on d7 is hanging.} 
