10. c4 {Welcome to the Dojo. A gorgeous piece sacrifice that aims to punish Black's lack of development and drafty king.10.exf6gxf611.Be3e5∓this is the computer's intention when it takes the pawn on d4. Please note that one only gains the confidence to play with such a drafty king if you have approval from a higher source!} 
