[White "Model Games"]
[Black "Yossef Glantzspiegel vs. Whiskeystud (2022)"]
[FEN "rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1"]
